{"tid":1303785,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[老任新機已出] Switch游戲太少? 任天堂最新發布的Switch宣傳片高調進行反駁!","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:54:53.000Z","uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"5489a5d41ff1949c54b092187b98398d014dc2b0","tid":1303785,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/videos/859469857760017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fvideos%2F859469857760017%2F&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=09f7f50b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/videos/859469857760017/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>#被批Switch游戲還是太少了 #逼到Nintendo森氣氣啦</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Switch上游戲還是太少了。&rdquo;不論國內還是國外，都有不少玩家在入手了Switch後發出了這樣的小抱怨，粉絲們也通常會拿幾款一方大作究竟如何耐玩去進行安撫，卻依舊沒有解決&ldquo;遊戲少&rdquo;這個疑問。而任天堂最新發布的Switch宣傳片則高調對此進行了反駁，<strong><ins>在接近兩年的時間裡，Switch上的遊戲其實已經接近2500款，能夠為不同類型的每個玩家都提供能夠享受的遊戲</ins></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n宣傳片的重點還是放在任天堂今年夏天到明年春季預定發售的作品序列上，包括了《精靈寶可夢：劍盾》、《火焰紋章：風花雪月》、《路易的鬼屋3》、《異界鎖鏈》、《勇者鬥惡龍S》、《漫威終極聯盟》、《二之國重製版》、《集合啦！動物森友會》等等。<br />\n<br />\n隨後<strong><ins>任天堂強調了宣傳片的標語，那就是遊戲陣容是&ldquo;為每個玩家所準備的&rdquo;。</ins></strong>的確，經過長時間的豐富產品流程，即使除去海量的真香冷飯，Switch上已經可以在每種主流遊戲中提供一款高知名度/精品作品了。而<strong><ins>隨著《巫師3》等原本難以想像的大作也要試水NS平台，其陣容庫真的不再貧瘠。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>雖然還沒有官宣，但種種跡象表明任天堂的下一代Switch，新型號版本已經離我們不遠了。</ins></strong>假如任天堂能夠為Switch帶來一次機能方面的大升級，相信以後NS的遊戲庫將會越來越豐富，或許能夠滿足更多追求畫面表現的玩家。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/auiVH_LCwiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FauiVH_LCwiw&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=90e1e7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/auiVH_LCwiw</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>[任天堂就是道路、真理、生命] 任天堂正考慮在中國以外的國家建立新的主機製造廠</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1301855/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1301855/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>任天堂正式發表「Nintendo Switch Lite」 9月發售, , 約$1500</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1303755/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1303755/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"38b67a1a86ed0d14c45ce9ba45d0fc93bcc31845","tid":1303785,"uid":46155,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"芒亨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854bab1584af565024bedee07634450c707df60d","tid":1303785,"uid":213142,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"問題根本唔係宣傳度<br />\n<br />\n佢地個腦到底係咪裝屎"},{"pid":"6f918750dbee3cc3b0772caa7128f60c9a2af3cf","tid":1303785,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"10 playable"},{"pid":"60dcf0eb9b898abfc2f1a983a54547caabcfe3f0","tid":1303785,"uid":138357,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"好多都舊game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又貴 我係steam買唔好？"},{"pid":"88a88c996a6bd1b2509394b495be162f1c3fcd42","tid":1303785,"uid":54878,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"有少少柒味"},{"pid":"3ffed44dca36a8c2cd5824d407817c1a3fa24a13","tid":1303785,"uid":111460,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"聞到陣精味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef032e4c14d35c0d4a35b4d28f362a28d4db9602","tid":1303785,"uid":32577,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"60dcf0eb9b898abfc2f1a983a54547caabcfe3f0","tid":1303785,"uid":138357,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"好多都舊game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又貴 我係steam買唔好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa